				<p class="text-xl text-primary font-semibold mb-6">
					Cloud Engineer | Kubernetes Maintainer
				</p>
				<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed" set:html={PROFESSIONAL_SUMMARY}>
				</p>
			</div>
			</div>
			<img
				src={Ava}
				alt="Urvashi Choubey"
				width="300"
				class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl mt-8 lg:mt-0"
			/>
		</div>

		<!-- Professional Experience Section -->
		<div id="experience" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Professional Experience</h2>
			<div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-lg">
				<div class="p-6">
					<div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6 flex-wrap gap-2">
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Cloud Engineer</h3>
							<p class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Fair Isaac India Software Private Limited (FICO)</p>
						</div>
						<span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-primary/10 text-primary">May 2022 - Present</span>
					</div>

					<!-- MFT System UI -->
					<div class="mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Managed File Transfer System UI</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-2">
							Leading the design and development of a Streamlit-based dashboard for FICO's Managed File Transfer platform, enabling internal teams to monitor transfers and manage workflows in real time.
						</p>
						<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mt-2">
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">Python Streamlit</span>
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">AWS ECS</span>
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">CloudWatch</span>
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">ALB</span>
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">GitHub Actions</span>
							<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600">IAM</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<hr class="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 my-4" />

					<!-- AWS Managed File Transfer System -->
					<div class="mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">AWS Managed File Transfer System</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-2">
							Co-developed a modular <a href="https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/storage/how-fico-modernizes-file-transfers-with-etl-automation-using-aws-transfer-family/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary underline font-medium">MFT architecture</a> composed of transfer, orchestration, and execution layers.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Designed for scalability and cost efficiency</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Implemented secure, production-grade integrations</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Built enterprise-ready file transfer workflows</span></li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<hr class="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 my-4" />

					<!-- Client-Focused Solution Development -->
					<div class="mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Client-Focused Solution Development</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-2">
							Worked directly with clients to understand business requirements and deliver tailored file transfer solutions.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Designed and provisioned secure S3-to-S3 transfer workflows</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Implemented end-to-end infrastructure with security best practices</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Delivered production-ready features directly used by clients</span></li>
						</ul>
						<p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mt-2 italic">
							This exposure helped me understand client expectations, solution design trade-offs, and real-world enterprise constraints.
						</p>
					</div>

					<hr class="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 my-4" />

					<!-- Kubernetes-Native Infrastructure -->
					<div class="mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Kubernetes-Native Infrastructure</h4>
