						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Enabled self-service infrastructure for developers</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Reduced provisioning time from ~2 weeks to 5‚Äì10 minutes</span></li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">‚Ä¢</span><span>Integrated with GitHub-based workflows</span></li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<hr class="border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 my-4" />

					<!-- Automation & CI/CD -->
					<div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Automation & CI/CD</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
							Built GitHub Actions workflows and automation pipelines to eliminate manual processes and improve deployment consistency.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Open Source Contributions Section with Timeline -->
		<div id="open-source" class="mb-12 scroll-mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Open Source Contributions</h2>

			<!-- Timeline -->
			<div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-lg mb-6">
